It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

<blockquote>Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>

...or something like this:

<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>

As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://fsdriving.themerex.net/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. <h4>What do I need to do before I take my road test?</h4>
Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. <ul>
 	<li>Obey the<span style="color: #419de6;"> <a style="color: #419de6;" href="#">learner permit restrictions</a></span> on where and when you may drive</li>
 	<li>Complete a 5-hour Pre-licensing Course or a high school or college Driver Education Course</li>
 	<li>Get an appropriate amount of supervised driving practice</li>
 	<li>if you are under age 18, you must wait at least six months from the date you received your learner permit to schedule your road test</li>
</ul>

<h4>What do I need to do before I take my road test?</h4>
Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.
<ul>
 	<li>Obey the<span style="color: #419de6;"> <a style="color: #419de6;" href="#">learner permit restrictions</a></span> on where and when you may drive</li>
 	<li>Complete a 5-hour Pre-licensing Course or a high school or college Driver Education Course</li>
 	<li>Get an appropriate amount of supervised driving practice</li>
 	<li>if you are under age 18, you must wait at least six months from the date you received your learner permit to schedule your road test</li>
</ul>

Neque porro quisquam est, qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, consectetur.[/vc_toggle][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row]";s:10:"post_title";s:3:"FAQ";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:3:"faq";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-03-02 14:59:58";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-03-02 14:59:58";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://fsdriving.themerex.net/?page_id=182";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:119;a:23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"184";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-01-12 11:22:08";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-01-12 11:22:08";s:12:"post_content";s:6958:"[vc_row full_width="stretch_row"][vc_column][vc_empty_space alter_height="large" hide_on_mobile=""][trx_sc_content title_align="center" width="none" title="Our Support Policy" scheme="inherit"][/trx_sc_content][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ul class="trx_addons_list trx_addons_list_check">
	<li>To get a pre-purchase advice, you may post in the theme’s forum.</li>
	<li>To get a response more promptly, you are recommended to use our Ticket-system.</li>
	<li>We try to answer your questions within 1-10 hours. However, if any delay occurs, it doesn’t mean that we forgot about you. Some of the issues require testing and analyzing, so we can resolve it effectively.</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ul class="trx_addons_list trx_addons_list_check">
	<li>Please note! We do not provide support, if you do not have the purchase code.</li>
	<li>Item support does not include:</li>
</ul>
<ol>
	<li>Customization and installation.</li>
	<li>Support for third party software and plugins.</li>
</ol>
[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row"][vc_column][vc_empty_space alter_height="huge" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1484507693839{background-color: #f6f7fb !important;}"][vc_column][vc_empty_space alter_height="large" hide_on_mobile=""][trx_sc_content title_align="center" width="none" title="How to use our Support System" description="ThemeRex technical support is always there to assist their users with all the technical questions regarding ThemeRex products.
" scheme="inherit"][/trx_sc_content][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1484507637967{background-color: #f6f7fb !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="298" img_size="523x301"][vc_empty_space hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ol>
	<li>In the ‘Item Details’ there is a clickable banner “Support Sys”, which leads you to tickets.</li>
	<li>Or you may simply follow this link: <a href="https://themerex.ticksy.com/">themerex.ticksy.com.</a></li>
	<li>Enter your purchase key and register in the system.</li>
	<li>To avoid a confusion, please use your own ThemeForest login in Support System.</li>
	<li>Fill out the ticket form.</li>
</ol>
[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1484507705220{background-color: #f6f7fb !important;}"][vc_column][vc_empty_space alter_height="huge" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row"][vc_column][vc_empty_space alter_height="large" hide_on_mobile=""][trx_sc_content title_align="center" width="none" title="How to find a purchase key" scheme="inherit"][/trx_sc_content][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="300" img_size="648x397"][vc_empty_space hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ul class="trx_addons_list trx_addons_list_check">
	<li>Open the “downloads” tab in your account.</li>
	<li>Find our theme in the list of products.</li>
	<li>Click “download” button, and in the drop-down menu select “license certificate &amp; purchase code”.</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1484507663831{background-color: #f6f7fb !important;}"][vc_column][vc_empty_space alter_height="large" hide_on_mobile=""][trx_sc_content title_align="center" width="none" title="Hosting" scheme="inherit"][/trx_sc_content][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1484507658135{background-color: #f6f7fb !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text]
<h4 class="sc_title sc_title_regular sc_align_center margin_top_small margin_bottom_small" style="text-align: center;">Recommended hostings:</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;">ThemeREX offers only the best products and services and recommends them to their customers. One of the most important services is HOSTING. Unlike any cheap hostings that usually have limited resources which causes many problems to the site owners, quality hosting gives a client a fair amount of resources sufficient for any website and any task. By using quality hosting you can rest assured that your site will work smoothly. If you happen to use such hosting with limited resources (e.g. GoDaddy!), you may experience issues with “one-click install” feature. In that case, you are always welcome to contact our support team to get qualified help.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://secure1.inmotionhosting.com/cgi-bin/gby/clickthru.cgi?id=themerex">http://www.inmotionhosting.com</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Get more than <strong>30% discount</strong> on a hosting plan.</p>

<h2>Dear Customers,</h2>
Information listed on this page will help you build your own website in the most effective way.
Our primary goal is developing a secure and customizable theme framework that meets the needs of the end user. Therefore, our customers are able to create websites using our templates as easy as 1-2-3! This process requires minimum knowledge of WordPress and coding, and extended documentation and our Support Team is always at your service. However, we ask you to keep in mind that sometimes issues occur not because of templates malfunction. There might be situations when it doesn't depend on us and the framework. For example, server settings, some extra functional that requires deep file customization, or additional plugins usage. And of course, and attempt to build a website in a very short amount of time.

Since we put a lot of effort, knowledge and devotion into creating quality products, we do not make smaller customization projects upon your requests. For such inquiries we recommend contacting our partner <strong><a href="https://mockingbird.ticksy.com/">Mockingbird Custom Website Studio</a>.</strong> They know our theme framework perfectly and have a highly-professional team of developers. The statistic shows that the majority of the customers that have contacted Mockingbird for customization were satisfied with the results and recommend the services to other users.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_separator style="dashed"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][trx_sc_title title_align="center" title="Our Customization Services" subtitle="CUSTOMIZATION"][vc_empty_space alter_height="small" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_column_text]
<ul class="trx_addons_list trx_addons_list_dot">
	<li><strong>Logo/company’s name replacement – $19</strong>
We will replace the template’s logo with yours on each of the template’s pages. Customer should provide logo in good quality in .PSD, .EPS, .AI or .CDR format</li>
	<li><strong>Advanced contact form for WordPress template – from $45 </strong>
Creating advanced contact form with your own fields with dropdowns / checkboxes / radio buttons</li>
	<li><strong>Installation – $39</strong>
Template will be installed to your server to look like in our on-line demo. Access to admin panel will be granted to you to manage your website</li>
	<li><strong>Contact form customization – $29</strong>
We’ll rename field’s names, add or remove no more than 2 text fields</li>
	<li><strong>Change fontello icon – from $19</strong></li>
	<li><strong>Custom page layout – from $30</strong></li>
	<li><strong>Woocommerce Shop page settings - from $45</strong></li>
	<li><strong>WordPress Website Migration/Transfer/Cloning - $49</strong></li>
	<li><strong>Language file localization - from$20</strong></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.8em; font-weight: 300;">If you need our assistance, feel free to submit a ticket for our professional team <a href="https://mockingbird.ticksy.com/">here</a></p>

<ul class="trx_addons_list_success trx_addons_list_success_circled">
	<li style="text-align: left;">Spam filtering plugin to keep your comments clean</li>
	<li style="text-align: left;">Google Analytics for ultimate traffic stats</li>
	<li style="text-align: left;">Plugin to change login page url in order to secure your website from hackers attacks</li>
	<li style="text-align: left;">Plugin for easy backup</li>
	<li style="text-align: left;">Installation service is not included in this pack</li>
</ul>
[/trx_sc_price][vc_empty_space height="" alter_height="small"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][trx_sc_price icon_type="fontawesome" title="Ready to use Website" subtitle="gold" scheme="default" price="$250" link="https://mockingbird.ticksy.com/" link_text="Submit a request"]

The template you have purchased from us will be customized with your logo, colors and content up to 6 pages (additional programming is not included). Finally, we will install it on your server.[/trx_sc_price][vc_empty_space height="" alter_height="small"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][trx_sc_price icon_type="fontawesome" title="Installation + Logo change" subtitle="regular" scheme="default" price="$49" link="https://mockingbird.ticksy.com/" link_text="Submit a request"]

	<li style="text-align: left;">We will replace the template’s logo with yours on each page of the template. Customers should provide logos in good quality in .PSD, .EPS, .Al, or .CDR format.</li>
